"Copy is usually best, fast and preserves full quality.\n"
"\n"
"Re-encoding slightly reduces quality but improves compatibility and can "
"reduce file size."
msgstr ""
"Copy is usually best, fast and preserves full quality.\n"
"\n"
"Re-encoding slightly reduces quality but improves compatibility and can "
"reduce file size."

